headline: Fiserv Announces the Appointment of Stephanie Cohen to Board of Directors
summary: MILWAUKEE, March 17, 2025--Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE: FI), a leading global provider of payments and financial services technology solutions, today announced the appointment of Stephanie Cohen to its Board of Directors.
